Package edu.mills.cs114.lab8

The classes necessary for CS 114/214 Lab 8, in which students modify an NFA solver so it is multi-threaded instead of single-threaded.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NFA
    A nondeterministic finite automaton.
    Solver
    A "solver" that tries to find a sequence of transitions from a given State to an accept state in a nondeterministic finite automaton (NFA).
    State
    A node in a non-deterministic finite state automaton (NFA).

Package edu.mills.cs114.lab8 Description

The classes necessary for CS 114/214 Lab 8, in which students modify an NFA solver so it is multi-threaded instead of single-threaded.
